# Artifacts Directory
# ==================
# Generated by 8-Model Scatter-Gather Research System
# Gen87.X3.1

This directory contains output artifacts from research runs:

## Files Generated

- `cloudevents.jsonl` - CloudEvents log (append-only)
- `consensus.json` - Full consensus result with metadata
- `consensus.md` - Human-readable consensus report
- `responses/port_*.json` - Raw responses from each model

Claims require 6/8 model agreement to reach consensus.
